" class=\"copied\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;  widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">&lt; img标记为源一个显式URL</span><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><span id=\"tran_31\" data-aligning=\"#tran_31,#src_31\" class=\"copied\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;  widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">*示例表单功能齐全</span><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><span id=\"tran_32\" data-aligning=\"#tran_32,#src_32\" class=\"copied\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;  widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">参考文档在文档目录中。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><span id=\"tran_33\" data-aligning=\"#tran_33,#src_33\" class=\"copied\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;  widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">请注意,包装PHPMailer-FE已经改变了。</span><span id=\"tran_34\" data-aligning=\"#tran_34,#src_34\" class=\"copied\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;  widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">PHPMailer-FE现在</span><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><span id=\"tran_35\" data-aligning=\"#tran_35,#src_35\" class=\"copied\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;  widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">_lib目录的根(像所有其他支持文件)。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><span id=\"tran_36\" data-aligning=\"#tran_36,#src_36\" class=\"copied\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;  widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">发现文档:http://www.worxware.com/kbn/?category_id=23</span><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: Tahoma, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"/><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>最后,解压phpmailer 到文件夹,里面包含详细的文档说明:</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\">IsSMTP();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;send&nbsp;via&nbsp;SMTP&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Host&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;......&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;SMTP&nbsp;servers&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;SMTPAuth&nbsp;=&nbsp;true;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;turn&nbsp;on&nbsp;SMTP&nbsp;authentication&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Username&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;yourmail&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;SMTP&nbsp;username&nbsp;&nbsp;注意：普通邮件认证不需要加&nbsp;@域名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Password&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;mailPassword&quot;;&nbsp;//&nbsp;SMTP&nbsp;password&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;From&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;1716771371@yourdomain.com&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;发件人邮箱&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;FromName&nbsp;=&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;管理员&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;发件人&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;CharSet&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;GB2312&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;这里指定字符集！&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Encoding&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;base64&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;AddAddress($sendto_email,&quot;username&quot;);&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;收件人邮箱和姓名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;AddReplyTo(&quot;yourmail@yourdomain.com&quot;,&quot;yourdomain.com&quot;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//$mail-&gt;WordWrap&nbsp;=&nbsp;50;&nbsp;//&nbsp;set&nbsp;word&nbsp;wrap&nbsp;换行字数&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//$mail-&gt;AddAttachment(&quot;/var/tmp/file.tar.gz&quot;);&nbsp;//&nbsp;attachment&nbsp;附件&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//$mail-&gt;AddAttachment(&quot;/tmp/image.jpg&quot;,&nbsp;&quot;new.jpg&quot;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;IsHTML(true);&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;send&nbsp;as&nbsp;HTML&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;邮件主题&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Subject&nbsp;=&nbsp;$subject;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;邮件内容&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Body&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[object&nbsp;Object]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[object&nbsp;Object]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I&nbsp;love&nbsp;php。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;AltBody&nbsp;=&quot;text/html&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(!$mail-&gt;Send())&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;邮件发送有误</pre><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><a href=\"http://sourceforge.net/projects/phpmailer/files/latest/download?source=files\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"下载地址PHPMAILER\">下载地址PHPMAILER</a><br/></p>',0,NULL,'2016-06-15 09:21','2016-06-15',0,1,0),(14,'几个同学一起学习.NET毒发生亡','1231231231','123123123','21213',0,NULL,'2016-06-15 09:21','2016-06-15',0,0,0),(15,'几个同学一起学习.NET毒发生亡','1231231231','123123123','132',0,NULL,'2016-06-15 09:21','2016-06-15',0,0,1),(16,'几个同学一起学习.NET毒发生亡','1231231231','123123123','23',0,NULL,'2016-06-15 09:21','2016-06-15',0,0,0),(17,'几个同学一起学习.NET毒发生亡','1231231231','123123123','1231231',0,NULL,'2016-06-15 09:21','2016-06-15',0,0,0),(18,'几个同学一起学习.NET毒发生亡','1231231231','123123123','123123',0,NULL,'2016-06-15 09:21','2016-06-15',0,1,0),(19,'几个同学一起学习.NET毒发生亡','1231231231','123123123','31231231',0,NULL,'2016-06-15 09:21','2016-06-15',0,0,1),(20,'几个同学一起学习.NET毒发生亡','1231231231','123123123','13',0,NULL,'2016-06-15 09:21','2016-06-15',0,0,0);
